'''Imagneto Dance Company''' is a [[Lagos|Lagos-based]] dance group owned and founded by [[Kaffy]], a [[Nigerian]] dance instructor and [[choreographer]].<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.nigeriafilms.com/news/26022/46/kaffy-set-for-another-imagneto-dance-day.html | title=KAFFY SET FOR ANOTHER 'IMAGNETO DANCE DAY' | work=Nigeria Films | publisher=Akin Omobose | date=13 March 2014 | accessdate=6 July 2015}}</ref> The group is well known for breaking the [[Guinness Book of World Records|Guinness Book of World Record]] for "Longest Dance Party" at the Nokia Silverbird Danceathon in 2006.<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.bellanaija.com/2012/11/10/bn-saturday-celebrity-interview-chilling-out-with-nigerias-guinness-world-record-holder-the-dance-queen-kaffy/ | title=BN Saturday Celebrity Interview: Chilling Out with Nigeria’s Guinness World Record Holder, the “Dance Queen” Kaffy! | publisher=Adeola Adeyemo | work=BellaNaija | date=10 November 2012 | accessdate=6 July 2015}}</ref>

